                |> range(start: 2023-07-28T12:05:02.393004+00:00, stop: 2023-07-28T14:05:02.393005+00:00)
                |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "Rack_3_Light")
                |> aggregateWindow(every: 1h, fn: mean, createEmpty: true)
                |> fill(column: "_value", usePrevious: true)
                |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: if exists r["_value"] then r["_value"] else 0.0}))
                |> difference(columns: ["_value"], keepFirst: false)
                |> first()
